### Test Candidates Endpoints

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api

### 1. Get all candidates
GET {{baseUrl}}/candidates
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Get candidate by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/candidates/1
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Create a new candidate
POST {{baseUrl}}/candidates
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Sophie",
  "lastName": "Marceau",
  "email": "sophie.marceau@example.com",
  "phone": "0612345690",
  "birthDate": "1993-04-12",
  "address": "10 Rue de Paris",
  "city": "Paris",
  "country": "France",
  "educationLevel": "Master",
  "lastDegree": "Master en Informatique",
  "yearsExperience": 4,
  "skills": "Java, Spring, Angular, Docker"
}

